                          <td>Circle with X inside</td>
                        </tr>
                      </tbody>
                    </table>
                    <div class="info-box gold" style="margin-top:14px;">
                      <span class="ib-icon">&#9888;</span>
                      <div><strong>Always read the legend first</strong> before interpreting any electrical floor plan. Symbol conventions can vary slightly between architects and electrical engineers.</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
